Key Match Events: Stephon Castle put up 22 points on efficient shooting
Anthony Davis racked up 40 points and 12 rebounds
LeBron James added 15 points and 16 rebounds
Post-Match Reflections: The Spurs have found a special player in Stephon Castle
Interior defense will be a big focus moving forward
The team's progress is obvious, and they might just be one of the most intriguing teams to watch as the season goes on
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Spurs struggled to slow down Anthony Davis and LeBron James
Victor Wembanyama had a tough time matching up physically
Zach Collins' limited minutes didn't help much
Others: The Spurs are 6-7 right now and a solid 5-3 at home
Interim head coach Mitch Johnson has been holding things down while Gregg Popovich is away
